      <title>迪拜房地产市场强劲反弹 但出现疲态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/dubai-s-world-beating-property-rally-shows-signs-of-strain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年，随着开发商纷纷涌入全球最大的房地产热潮之一，迪拜将再次出现耀眼的新塔楼和别墅社区。然而，越来越多的迹象表明，创纪录的房价涨势正在放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/dubai-s-world-beating-property-rally-shows-signs-of-strain</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
